<h1><span class="text-gradient">博主分类</span></h1>
<h2>欢迎收看各种频道</h2>
<p>这是我搜集的资源。</p>
<p class="instructions">
    "发现多元声音：本网页汇集各领域博主，从生活点滴到专业知识，带你领略多彩视角。"
</p>
<ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
    <Card
        href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Au411h7P4/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click"
        title="学习类"
        body="探索知识的海洋，跟随博主的脚步，一起学习新知，提升自我。"
    />
    <Card
        href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1eC411p73m/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click/"
        title="技术类"
        body="深入技术前沿，了解最新科技动态，与技术大牛一起探讨未来趋势。"
    />
    <Card
        href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Fg4y1m7fU/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click"
        title="穿搭类"
        body="时尚不止于外表，跟随穿搭博主，发现适合自己的风格，展现个性魅力。"
    />
    <Card
        href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV19P4y1D7qB/?spm_id_from=333.337.search-card.all.click"
        title="美食探底类"
        body="品味各地美食，探索食材背后的故事，与美食博主一起享受舌尖上的旅行。"
    />
</ul>

<style>
    body {
        background-image: url("https://example.com/new-background-image.jpg");
        opacity: 0.8;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
    }
    main {
        margin: auto;
        padding: 1rem;
        width: 800px;
        max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
        color: white;
        font-size: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }
    nav {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        padding: 1rem;
    }
    nav a {
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    .astro-a {
        position: absolute;
        top: -32px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translatex(-50%);
        width: 220px;
        height: auto;
        z-index: -1;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        color: white;
    }
    h2 {
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
    }
    p {
        color: white;
    }
    .text-gradient {
        background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-size: 400%;
        background-position: 0%;
    }
    .instructions {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 25%);
        background: linear-gradient(
            rgba(var(--accent-dark), 66%),
            rgba(var(--accent-dark), 33%)
        );
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: white;
    }
    .instructions code {
        font-size: 0.8em;
        font-weight: bold;
        background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 12%);
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 0.3em 0.4em;
    }
    .instructions strong {
        color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
    }
    .link-card-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 0;
    }
</style>
